PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Public Works and Government Services of HILARY JUDITH GOLDENBERG, of Toronto, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Royal Canadian Mint to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Charles F.M. Ross, whose term has expired.
